Magdalena Stoyanova Georgieva (Bulgarian) (amụrụ na 7 Disemba 1962 na Plovdiv, Bulgaria) bụ onye ọkwọ ụgbọ mmiri si Bulgaria.

Ọ ghọrọ onye mmeri ụwa nke otu sculls na 1987 Asọmpi ịkwọ ụgbọ mmiri nke ụwa na Copenhagen, Denmark. Otu afọ mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, ọ sonyeere Bulgaria na 1988 Olimpik oge okpomọkụ nke e mere na Seoul, South Korea na otu ihe omume sculls ebe ọ mechara na nke atọ.
